││ a                            Open Add modal                                ││
││ r                            Open Remove confirmation                      ││
││ R                            Open Rename modal                             ││
││ i                            Open Import modal                             ││
││ e                            Open Export modal                             ││
││ /                            Focus search bar                              ││
││ Tab / Shift-Tab              Cycle focus between search bar and list       ││
││ Ctrl-N / Ctrl-P              In modals: next / previous control            ││
││ p                            Open Passphrase modal                         ││
││ s                            Open Settings modal                           ││
││ ?                            Open Help overlay                             ││
││ Esc                          Close modal / overlay / search; quit dead-end ││
